atedEnglishLine":"I'm begging you...)"}, {"lineNumber":199451,"originalJapaneseLine":"（わたしの声が、きこえる……あなたに……","translatedEnglishLine":"(My voice can be heard... by you..."}, {"lineNumber":199452,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おねがいが、あります……）","translatedEnglishLine":"I have a request...)"}, {"lineNumber":199453,"originalJapaneseLine":"（どうか……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Please...)"}, {"lineNumber":199454,"originalJapaneseLine":"（わたしをころして……）","translatedEnglishLine":"(Kill me...)"}, {"lineNumber":199455,"originalJapaneseLine":"…………","translatedEnglishLine":"........"}, {"lineNumber":199456,"originalJapaneseLine":"……","translatedEnglishLine":"..."}, {"lineNumber":199457,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなたはゆっくりと目を覚ました。","translatedEnglishLine":"You slowly opened your eyes."}, {"lineNumber":199458,"originalJapaneseLine":"パチパチと瞼を開きながら周囲を見渡す。","translatedEnglishLine":"Blinking your eyelids, you looked around."}, {"lineNumber":199459,"originalJapaneseLine":"どこかホテルの一室のような場所にあなたはいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"You found yourself in what seemed to be a hotel room."}, {"lineNumber":199460,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………。」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""}, {"lineNumber":199461,"originalJapaneseLine":"何か不思議な夢を見ていた気がする。","translatedEnglishLine":"You feel like you had some strange dream."}, {"lineNumber":199462,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おーっ、起きたか、＜エール＞！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh! You woke up, <Yell>!\""}, {"lineNumber":199463,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああ、良かった。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, good."}, {"lineNumber":199464,"originalJapaneseLine":"　これで一安心だすなあ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Now I can rest easy.\""}, {"lineNumber":199465,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちゃんと記憶はハッキリしてるか？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Is your memory clear?"}, {"lineNumber":199466,"originalJapaneseLine":"　何があったか覚えてるか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Do you remember what happened?\""}, {"lineNumber":199467,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………。」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""}, {"lineNumber":199468,"originalJapaneseLine":"「記憶がおぼろげだすか？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Is your memory hazy?"}, {"lineNumber":199469,"originalJapaneseLine":"　半分気絶していたようなもんだし仕方ないだすな」","translatedEnglishLine":"You were half unconscious, so it's understandable.\""}, {"lineNumber":199470,"originalJapaneseLine":"「まあ、思い出したくないだけかもな……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well, maybe you just don't want to remember..."}, {"lineNumber":199471,"originalJapaneseLine":"　俺だって正直クエルプランの中は","translatedEnglishLine":"Honestly, even I get chills thinking about inside Quelpuran."}, {"lineNumber":199472,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今、思い出してもゾッとするぜ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Even now, remembering that sends shivers down my spine.\""}, {"lineNumber":199473,"originalJapaneseLine":"「人に魔物に天使まで、ぜーんぶあの中にいて……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Humans, monsters, even angels— every single one is inside there..."}, {"lineNumber":199474,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おそらく今までに飲み込んだ全ての生き物が","translatedEnglishLine":"Probably every creature it ever swallowed"}, {"lineNumber":199475,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あの中にいるんだぜ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"is inside there...\""}, {"lineNumber":199476,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そうだすな……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That's right..."}, {"lineNumber":199477,"originalJapaneseLine":"　おら達もあのまま二度と出られなかったかも……","translatedEnglishLine":"We might never have come out if it weren't for..."}, {"lineNumber":199478,"originalJapaneseLine":"「でも、そこをダークランス様に助けられただす」","translatedEnglishLine":"Dark Rance saved us at that point.\""}, {"lineNumber":199479,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うぅん、本当に立派に成長なされただすなぁ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, you've truly grown into a fine person...\""}, {"lineNumber":199480,"originalJapaneseLine":"「んで、クエルプランから出て来た俺達は、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"And then, after we came out of Quelpuran,"}, {"lineNumber":199481,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんとびっくり皆の母ちゃん達に助けられたんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"to our surprise, everyone’s mothers helped us.\""}]}

